CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, November 10, 1956, pg. A16 reads: "The Working Scene of the Paree Salon show the new open working arrangements where the beauticians will make milady handsome from nine in morning until ten at night."
TitMainTitle: Interior of Paree Beauty Salon with striped linoleum floor, flowers for Grand Opening in entryway, and snake plants in planters
